---
title: Easy Golden Chicken & Roast Kumara Toss with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Kumara is very hard to resist when it’s roasted, those tender, orange pieces have a touch of smokiness and go perfectly when
joined by other roasted veggies and a creamy pesto yet spiced chicken. Dig in and enjoy!

